{"div":{"@":{"xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","type":"article","xml:id":"MG-1677-07_093","resp":"mercure","copyOf":"JLB-MG-1677-07_095"},"#":[{"head":{"value":"[Epistre en Vers de M. de Ramboüillet à Monsieur le Prince de Marsillac]","id":"/div/#[0]/head"}},{"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Le Nouveau Mercure galant","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/title"},"#1":{"value":", juillet 1677 (tome V), p. 93-101","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#1"},"note":{"@resp":"editor","#":{"value":"Il existe une autre édition parisienne, réalisée \"Suivant la Copie imprimée\" par Guillaume de Luyne, dont la pagination diffère.","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/note/#"}},"#2":{"value":".","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#2"}}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"Voyez-le encor, Madame, dans cette Lettre de M","id":"/div/#[2]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/#[2]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" de Ramboüillet à Monsieur le Prince de Marsillac Grand-Maistre de la Garderobe, Monsieur de Breteüil l’a leuë au Roy, à qui elle n’a pas déplû, &amp; je croirois vous dérober un plaisir, si je negligeois à vous l’envoyer.","id":"/div/#[2]/p/#2"}}},{"quote":{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"A MONSIEUR ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"LE PRINCE DE ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"MARSILLAC. ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Epistre.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/label/#[6]/hi/#"}}}]},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au lieu de jeûner le Caresme,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’estre avec un visage blême,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A faire vos Devotions,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vacquer à vos Stations,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce temps vous avez fait rage","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Parmy le sang &amp; le carnage,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous n’avez, malgré les hazards,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Songé qu’à forcer des Ramparts ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez pris trois grandes Villes,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Flamans les plus seurs aziles ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mesme vous avez fait périr","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ceux qui venoient les secourir,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Puny leur audace insolente,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans une Bataille sanglante,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce que les plus grands Conquerans","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A peine eussent fait en quatre ans.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[16]/#"},"hi":[{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[16]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":", l’ame de ces merveilles","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[16]/hi[1]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui n’eurent jamais de pareilles,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trouve maintenant à propos","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[18]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que les corps prennent du repos,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[19]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il a bien voulu leur permettre","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[20]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelque sejour pour se remettre.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[21]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy cependant fait mille tours,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’ame veille, elle agit toûjours,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et repasse sur toute chose,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pendant que le corps se repose.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais on dit que dans peu de temps","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous allez vous remmettre aux champs ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[27]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où Diable allez-vous donc encore ?","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est-ce au Nort, est-ce vers l’Aurore ?","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[29]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voulez-vous vous mettre sur l’eau,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[30]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et passer la Mer sans Vaisseau ?","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[31]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Dauphins de la Mer Baltique,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[32]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Baleines du Pole Arctique,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[33]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"(Ma foy vous n’aurez qu’à vouloir)","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[34]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Viendront vos ordres recevoir,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[35]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sur le Zelandois rivage,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[36]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous mettront, Canon &amp; Bagage.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ce n’est pas si grand’chose enfin,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous avez bien passé le Rhin,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cette Barriere si terrible,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont le passage est si pénible,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que Rome maistresse de tout,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A peine en vint jadis à bout.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ayant","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[44]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[44]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"à vostre teste,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[44]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous n’aurez rien qui vous arreste,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ce Héros tout réüssit,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout luy succede, tout luy rit.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est par là que ceux dont les veuës","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne sont pas assez étenduës,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Exaltent autant son bonheur","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que sa prudence &amp; sa valeur,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais ce qu’ils disent, bagatelles.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors que les Ministres fidelles,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont avec soin on a fait choix,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sont au dessus de leurs Emplois ;","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’avecque justice on dispense,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[56]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et la peine &amp; la récompense,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[57]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on sçait toutes choses prévoir,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[58]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A tous les accidens pourvoir,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[59]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que jamais on ne viole","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[60]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Don sacré de sa parole,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[61]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avec ces talens merveilleux,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[62]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est bien aisé d’estre heureux.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[63]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Cependant pour trop entreprendre,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[64]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous pourriez plus perdre que prendre :","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[65]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est vray qu’il faut que chacun","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[66]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Contribuë au bonheur commun.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[67]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On doit sacrifier sa vie","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[68]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A la gloire de sa Patrie.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[69]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi, Seigneur, malgré les coups","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[70]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Rhin vit tomber sur Vous,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[71]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous les jours une ardeur nouvelle","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[72]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous fait exposer de plus belle.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[73]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais il est bon de regarder,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[74]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il ne faut pas tout hazarder,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[75]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et que les Testes couronnées","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[76]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Doivent au moins estre épargnées.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[77]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comment souffrez-vous que le Roy","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[78]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"(Je n’y pense point sans effroy)","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[79]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Soit à toute heure aux mousquetades,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[80]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Toûjours en bute aux canonades ?","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[81]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous, Seigneur, qui matin &amp; soir","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[82]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avez le bonheur de le voir,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[83]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous sçavez, &amp; devez luy dire,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[84]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"(Quoy que des Dieux son sang il tire,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[85]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il soit le plus grand des Héros,)","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[86]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il est pourtant de chair &amp; d’os,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[87]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et qu’il a besoin d’une armure","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[88]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La mieux trempée &amp; la plus dure.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[89]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[90]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Philippe","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[90]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"n’en eust point mis,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[90]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’eust pas sur ses ennemis","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[91]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans cette Bataille fameuse","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[92]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Remporté la Victoire heureuse,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[93]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et nous verrions dans la douleur,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[94]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Madame qui rit de bon cœur.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[95]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’armure pourtant la meilleure,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[96]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’empesche pas qu’on n’y demeure.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[97]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Canon est encor plus fort,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[98]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Turenne en a senty l’effort,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[99]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[100]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[100]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"sçait mieux que personne,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[100]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que tout cede où le Boulet donne.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[101]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ainsi vous devez tout oser","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[102]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour l’empescher de s’exposer.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[103]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui doit toûjours estre le Maistre,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[104]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En ce point ne doit jamais l’estre.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[105]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Le plus seur est de revenir,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[106]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rien n’a droit de vous retenir","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[107]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors que des Beautez desolées,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[108]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’ennuis loin de vous accablées,","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[109]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne les finiront que le jour","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[110]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’elles vous verront de retour.","id":"/div/#[3]/quote/lg/l[111]/#"}}]}}},{"p":{"value":"Cet Article seroit mal finy, si je n’y joignois ces Vers qui ont esté chantez devant le Roy avec une entiere satisfaction de tous ceux qui ont eu le plaisir de les entendre.","id":"/div/#[4]/p"}},{"quote":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Grand Roy, fameux Héros à qui tout est soûmis,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tremblerons-nous toûjours comme vos Ennemis ?","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne pourrons-nous jamais apprendre sans alarmes,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’étonnant succés de vos armes ?","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Laissez porter la guerre en cent Climats divers,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sans vous exposer davantage ;","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais vous serez plutost Maistre de l’Univers,","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que de vostre Courage.","id":"/div/#[5]/quote/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"Ces Paroles sont de M","id":"/div/#[6]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/#[6]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" de Frontiniere. Il est si connu de toutes les Personnes de qualité qui ont le goût des bonnes choses, qu’on ne sçauroit mieux loüer ce qu’il fait, qu’en disant qu’il en est l’Autheur.","id":"/div/#[6]/p/#2"}}}]}}